query: WITH entities AS (SELECT reference, id FROM withdrawals WHERE (COALESCE((reference, id) < ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY reference DESC, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: WithdrawalId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN withdrawal_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.reference desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
